# type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: About/whatsnew.xml:735
msgid ""
"Added new <link linkend=\"configuringnagios-configcgi-lock_author_names"
"\">lock_author_names</link> option to prevent alteration of author names "
"when users submit comments, acknowledgements, and scheduled downtime."
